WEBVTT

00:04:59.614 --> 00:05:00.940
In fact, one study found

00:05:00.964 --> 00:05:02.988
that if you deploy to Iraq or Afghanistan,

00:05:03.012 --> 00:05:06.432
you're actually slightly less likely
to commit suicide later.

00:05:08.626 --> 00:05:10.896
I studied anthropology in college.

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:13.939
I did my fieldwork
on the Navajo reservation.

00:05:13.963 --> 00:05:17.358
I wrote a thesis on Navajo
long-distance runners.

00:05:18.473 --> 00:05:22.477
And recently, while
I was researching PTSD,

00:05:23.501 --> 00:05:25.606
I had this thought.

00:05:26.325 --> 00:05:29.404
I thought back to the work
I did when I was young,

00:05:29.428 --> 00:05:33.497
and I thought, I bet the Navajo,
the Apache, the Comanche --